Text.SourceString: You've arrived, my two-legged friend. Let me guess... <PlayerName>$Player</>, is it?//<portrait=happy>The journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step. You must be ready to take that step.
Text.LocalizedString: You've arrived, my two-legged friend. Let me guess... <PlayerName>$Player</>, is it?//<portrait=happy>The journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step. You must be ready to take that step.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> has seen it all...but these slimes...they're from the beyond.//This kind...<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> has not seen before.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> has seen it all...but these slimes...they're from the beyond.//This kind...<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> has not seen before.

Text.SourceString: The spirit world whispers, and we must listen.//Even if sometimes, all they're asking for is a cup of tea.
Text.LocalizedString: The spirit world whispers, and we must listen.//Even if sometimes, all they're asking for is a cup of tea.

Text.SourceString: Fear not, my two-legged fish friend, for the Queen may hesitate now, but rest assured, she'll come swimming around eventually.
Text.LocalizedString: Fear not, my two-legged fish friend, for the Queen may hesitate now, but rest assured, she'll come swimming around eventually.

Text.SourceString: This arrangement doesn't shock me, nothing surprises <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s ancient spirit.
Text.LocalizedString: This arrangement doesn't shock me, nothing surprises <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s ancient spirit.

Text.SourceString: This is the beginning of something great.//<portrait=normal>If I were a gambling fish, I'd bet my jaw-dropping prized possession, this jaw, on it.
Text.LocalizedString: This is the beginning of something great.//<portrait=normal>If I were a gambling fish, I'd bet my jaw-dropping prized possession, this jaw, on it.

Text.SourceString: It is worth nothing, oh, I know... <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s wealth lies not in material gold but in the depths of a compassionate heart.
Text.LocalizedString: It is worth nothing, oh, I know... <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s wealth lies not in material gold but in the depths of a compassionate heart.

Text.SourceString: Pray tell, what's the plan, <PlayerName>$Player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Pray tell, what's the plan, <PlayerName>$Player</>?

Text.SourceString: The King, an exemplar of wisdom, once again made the right call.
Text.LocalizedString: The King, an exemplar of wisdom, once again made the right call.

Text.SourceString: Two legs, why so many?
Text.LocalizedString: Two legs, why so many?

Text.SourceString: You've appeared in my visions many times...yes, indeed you have.//In a sense, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> has known you for quite a while. We just hadn't conversed.
Text.LocalizedString: You've appeared in my visions many times...yes, indeed you have.//In a sense, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> has known you for quite a while. We just hadn't conversed.

Text.SourceString: That name of yours, quite an eyebrow-raiser! Is there a grand place named <PlayerName>$Player</> up the shore?
Text.LocalizedString: That name of yours, quite an eyebrow-raiser! Is there a grand place named <PlayerName>$Player</> up the shore?

Text.SourceString: Or are you named after a magnificent ancient beast?
Text.LocalizedString: Or are you named after a magnificent ancient beast?

Text.SourceString: Ah, I sense a great energy surrounding you.//The path you tread is filled with both challenges and Goddess' blessings.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, I sense a great energy surrounding you.//The path you tread is filled with both challenges and Goddess' blessings.

Text.SourceString: Listen closely, for the Goddess resides in water.//Her presence may be subtle, but it lingers within every ripple.
Text.LocalizedString: Listen closely, for the Goddess resides in water.//Her presence may be subtle, but it lingers within every ripple.

Text.SourceString: Now, <PlayerName>$Player</>, tread carefully, for she keeps a watchful eye on your actions.//<portrait=happy>AHAHAHA! I'm just pulling your fin! Nobody cares, do what you want...just don't let <NpcName>Semeru</> sees your shenanigans.
Text.LocalizedString: Now, <PlayerName>$Player</>, tread carefully, for she keeps a watchful eye on your actions.//<portrait=happy>AHAHAHA! I'm just pulling your fin! Nobody cares, do what you want...just don't let <NpcName>Semeru</> sees your shenanigans.

Text.SourceString: King Krakatoa, long may he reign... He's a leader with a calm and steady mind.
Text.LocalizedString: King Krakatoa, long may he reign... He's a leader with a calm and steady mind.

Text.SourceString: Under his ruling, the energy of the Kingdom feels balanced, harmonious.
Text.LocalizedString: Under his ruling, the energy of the Kingdom feels balanced, harmonious.

Text.SourceString: In the whispers of the wind, I hear the spirits speak highly of our King Krakatoa.//I hear them... I relay their words.
Text.LocalizedString: In the whispers of the wind, I hear the spirits speak highly of our King Krakatoa.//I hear them... I relay their words.

Text.SourceString: Our kind...and yours, land-dwellers, must be reminded from time to time.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> is here to do that job.
Text.LocalizedString: Our kind...and yours, land-dwellers, must be reminded from time to time.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> is here to do that job.

Text.SourceString: Princess Miranjani, she holds the wisdom of the ancients within her, oh yes, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> knows.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> sees all...
Text.LocalizedString: Princess Miranjani, she holds the wisdom of the ancients within her, oh yes, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> knows.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> sees all...

Text.SourceString: What I observe, is she also possesses the curiosity of a young one.
Text.LocalizedString: What I observe, is she also possesses the curiosity of a young one.

Text.SourceString: Our Queen understands the weight of tradition.//<portrait=happy>The only individual <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> perceives to have a heart stronger than the King's...and I'm not talking about her ability to outswim a dolphin!//No, I did not.
Text.LocalizedString: Our Queen understands the weight of tradition.//<portrait=happy>The only individual <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> perceives to have a heart stronger than the King's...and I'm not talking about her ability to outswim a dolphin!//No, I did not.

Text.SourceString: Word travels fast in the underwater world, and you, my two-legged fish friend, the talk of the kelp forest.
Text.LocalizedString: Word travels fast in the underwater world, and you, my two-legged fish friend, the talk of the kelp forest.

Text.SourceString: My vision unfolds before me, step by step...oh, how incredible.
Text.LocalizedString: My vision unfolds before me, step by step...oh, how incredible.

Text.SourceString: Hold onto your seashells! The kelps are richer in color.//This is what balance looks like.
Text.LocalizedString: Hold onto your seashells! The kelps are richer in color.//This is what balance looks like.

Text.SourceString: I choose silence as my companion today.//Let the stillness speak volumes in place of my words.
Text.LocalizedString: I choose silence as my companion today.//Let the stillness speak volumes in place of my words.

Text.SourceString: I must depart. Bye-bye now.
Text.LocalizedString: I must depart. Bye-bye now.

Text.SourceString: Time calls me away. Until we meet again.
Text.LocalizedString: Time calls me away. Until we meet again.

Text.SourceString: Ah, the darkness, gone it is! Clear are the waters, and free are the hearts.//My foresight has been proven true.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, the darkness, gone it is! Clear are the waters, and free are the hearts.//My foresight has been proven true.

Text.SourceString: The end of a chapter, it is. From murky depths, a brighter kingdom emerges.//Thank you, my friend.
Text.LocalizedString: The end of a chapter, it is. From murky depths, a brighter kingdom emerges.//Thank you, my friend.

Text.SourceString: THE SLIMES HAVE VANISHED!
Text.LocalizedString: THE SLIMES HAVE VANISHED!

Text.SourceString: As a testament of my gratitude, I would offer you my jaw necklace.//<portrait=happy>However, I regretfully confess that my attempts to sell it yielded only two shells and three strips of wild kelp.
Text.LocalizedString: As a testament of my gratitude, I would offer you my jaw necklace.//<portrait=happy>However, I regretfully confess that my attempts to sell it yielded only two shells and three strips of wild kelp.

Text.SourceString: It's a pity, really, because it's lovely, yet nobody seems to see its beauty.//<portrait=happy>Sometimes <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> sees too much.
Text.LocalizedString: It's a pity, really, because it's lovely, yet nobody seems to see its beauty.//<portrait=happy>Sometimes <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> sees too much.

Text.SourceString: All of these...ignore them, my friend. You and your two legs, just pay them no mind.//Being an oracle is a process that happens within...deep within my soul. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> doesn't require the assistance of worldly items.//The trinkets and baubles...they're just here to add a splash of color to the place.
Text.LocalizedString: All of these...ignore them, my friend. You and your two legs, just pay them no mind.//Being an oracle is a process that happens within...deep within my soul. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> doesn't require the assistance of worldly items.//The trinkets and baubles...they're just here to add a splash of color to the place.

Text.LocalizedString: Word travels fast in the underwater world, and you, my two-legged fish friend, the talk of the kelp forest.

Text.LocalizedString: I must depart. Bye-bye now.

Text.SourceString: Time calls me away. Until we meet again.
Text.LocalizedString: Time calls me away. Until we meet again.

Text.SourceString: All of these...ignore them, my friend. You and your two legs, just pay them no mind.//Being an oracle is a process that happens within...deep within my soul. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> doesn't require the assistance of worldly items.//The trinkets and baubles...they're just here to add a splash of color to the place.
Text.LocalizedString: All of these...ignore them, my friend. You and your two legs, just pay them no mind.//Being an oracle is a process that happens within...deep within my soul. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> doesn't require the assistance of worldly items.//The trinkets and baubles...they're just here to add a splash of color to the place.

Text.SourceString: In the vast ocean of life, it is rare to find a current that flows in harmony with one's own.//<portrait=normal>You, my friend, are like that rare current, aligning perfectly with the tides of <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s spirit.
Text.LocalizedString: In the vast ocean of life, it is rare to find a current that flows in harmony with one's own.//<portrait=normal>You, my friend, are like that rare current, aligning perfectly with the tides of <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s spirit.

Text.SourceString: To have a friend in you is like finding a treasure hidden beneath the waves.//Your presence brings light to the depths of my oceanic heart.
Text.LocalizedString: To have a friend in you is like finding a treasure hidden beneath the waves.//Your presence brings light to the depths of my oceanic heart.

Text.SourceString: In your company, I feel the calm of a gentle sea.
Text.LocalizedString: In your company, I feel the calm of a gentle sea.

Text.SourceString: The ocean whispers secrets to those who listen. In our friendship, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> hears those whispers more clearly.//Two-legged wonder, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> refers.
Text.LocalizedString: The ocean whispers secrets to those who listen. In our friendship, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> hears those whispers more clearly.//Two-legged wonder, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> refers.

Text.SourceString: You, <PlayerName>$Player</>, are a great listener. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> is used to listening, but sometimes, she must speak. And you, you provide the ears.
Text.LocalizedString: You, <PlayerName>$Player</>, are a great listener. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> is used to listening, but sometimes, she must speak. And you, you provide the ears.

Text.SourceString: Seeing you here is a good sight.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> woke up foreseeing this very moment. Hello, my friend.
Text.LocalizedString: Seeing you here is a good sight.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> woke up foreseeing this very moment. Hello, my friend.

Text.SourceString: Greetings, my dear land friend.
Text.LocalizedString: Greetings, my dear land friend.

Text.SourceString: How are you, my friend?
Text.LocalizedString: How are you, my friend?

Text.SourceString: You look extra slimy today, my friend – a compliment, a high compliment indeed.
Text.LocalizedString: You look extra slimy today, my friend – a compliment, a high compliment indeed.

Text.SourceString: This vision, like a turbulent sea, disturbs <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s tranquility.
Text.LocalizedString: This vision, like a turbulent sea, disturbs <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s tranquility.

Text.SourceString: In dreams, the ocean often whispers truths. This one screams of danger. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> feels it in her waters.
Text.LocalizedString: In dreams, the ocean often whispers truths. This one screams of danger. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> feels it in her waters.

Text.SourceString: My heart is heavy like the depths. What if this vision is a tide foretelling a dire event?
Text.LocalizedString: My heart is heavy like the depths. What if this vision is a tide foretelling a dire event?

Text.SourceString: The red splash haunts <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>. It is a sign, a beacon in the night. We must uncover its meaning.
Text.LocalizedString: The red splash haunts <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>. It is a sign, a beacon in the night. We must uncover its meaning.

Text.SourceString: Your aid in this mystery, like a guiding star, is invaluable. Together, let us navigate these dark waters.
Text.LocalizedString: Your aid in this mystery, like a guiding star, is invaluable. Together, let us navigate these dark waters.

Text.SourceString: Our quest leads us through murky waters. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s intuition says <NPCName>Princess Miranjani</> is key to this enigma.
Text.LocalizedString: Our quest leads us through murky waters. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s intuition says <NPCName>Princess Miranjani</> is key to this enigma.

Text.SourceString: In every corner, in every shadow, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> seeks signs.
Text.LocalizedString: In every corner, in every shadow, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> seeks signs.

Text.SourceString: This journey, like a meandering river, takes unexpected turns. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> senses we are close.
Text.LocalizedString: This journey, like a meandering river, takes unexpected turns. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> senses we are close.

Text.SourceString: Your presence, like a steady current, gives <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> strength. We must find the one who mirrors my dream.
Text.LocalizedString: Your presence, like a steady current, gives <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> strength. We must find the one who mirrors my dream.

Text.SourceString: Ah, the sea's riddle unravels! <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> sees now - not all visions foretell doom.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, the sea's riddle unravels! <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> sees now - not all visions foretell doom.

Text.SourceString: We've sailed through mist and found clear skies. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> thanks you, friend, for charting these waters with her.
Text.LocalizedString: We've sailed through mist and found clear skies. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> thanks you, friend, for charting these waters with her.

Text.SourceString: Miranjani's cry, like a seagull's squawk, is loud but harmless. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s heart lightens.
Text.LocalizedString: Miranjani's cry, like a seagull's squawk, is loud but harmless. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s heart lightens.

Text.SourceString: The bounty of the sea offers us a feast. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> can guide you in preparing the tenderest octopus stew, but not today; the time isn't right.
Text.LocalizedString: The bounty of the sea offers us a feast. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> can guide you in preparing the tenderest octopus stew, but not today; the time isn't right.

Text.SourceString: To taste the sea is to understand its essence.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> recommends seaweed, a gift from the ocean's garden.
Text.LocalizedString: To taste the sea is to understand its essence.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> recommends seaweed, a gift from the ocean's garden.

Text.SourceString: For a troubled mind, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> suggests a cup of sea cucumber tea — it's like a hug from a friendly octopus, but for your insides.
Text.LocalizedString: For a troubled mind, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> suggests a cup of sea cucumber tea — it's like a hug from a friendly octopus, but for your insides.

Text.SourceString: Herbs like lavender and lemon balm, under <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s care, become potions to soothe the weariest of souls. Are you a worried soul, friend?
Text.LocalizedString: Herbs like lavender and lemon balm, under <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s care, become potions to soothe the weariest of souls. Are you a worried soul, friend?

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> brews a tea of elderflower and nettle, a tonic that whispers of ancient healing secrets. Can you hear their whispers, friend, calling to <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s spirit?
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> brews a tea of elderflower and nettle, a tonic that whispers of ancient healing secrets. Can you hear their whispers, friend, calling to <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s spirit?

Text.SourceString: This herbal remedy, a blend of sea fennel and rosehips, is <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s gift for your vitality.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> will send some over to our barrack friends, to lessen their grumps.
Text.LocalizedString: This herbal remedy, a blend of sea fennel and rosehips, is <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s gift for your vitality.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> will send some over to our barrack friends, to lessen their grumps.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> finds stillness in the rhythm of the waves. Let their constant flow guide your meditation.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> finds stillness in the rhythm of the waves. Let their constant flow guide your meditation.

Text.SourceString: Close your eyes and breathe with the tides. Inhale peace, exhale turmoil.
Text.LocalizedString: Close your eyes and breathe with the tides. Inhale peace, exhale turmoil.

Text.SourceString: To be present, as <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> knows, is to listen to the sea's song in every shell, every grain of sand.
Text.LocalizedString: To be present, as <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> knows, is to listen to the sea's song in every shell, every grain of sand.

Text.SourceString: A dear friend of mine, Shrimpy, taught me that.
Text.LocalizedString: A dear friend of mine, Shrimpy, taught me that.

Text.SourceString: The moon's dance with the sea reveals much. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> reads the tides like the stars – a map of destiny.
Text.LocalizedString: The moon's dance with the sea reveals much. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> reads the tides like the stars – a map of destiny.

Text.SourceString: As the full moon brightens the sea, so do the ocean spirits illuminate our path with astrological wisdom.
Text.LocalizedString: As the full moon brightens the sea, so do the ocean spirits illuminate our path with astrological wisdom.

Text.SourceString: Oh yes, we delve into the sky as deeply as we explore the sea, for they are one and the same.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh yes, we delve into the sky as deeply as we explore the sea, for they are one and the same.

Text.SourceString: The stars and sea are our ancient guides.
Text.LocalizedString: The stars and sea are our ancient guides.

Text.SourceString: Each lunar phase holds a message, yet none has reached down here.//<portrait=normal>Perhaps a swim above will help us discern the whispers of the moon.
Text.LocalizedString: Each lunar phase holds a message, yet none has reached down here.//<portrait=normal>Perhaps a swim above will help us discern the whispers of the moon.

Text.SourceString: In days like these, it reminds <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> of a past home, Atlantoria – the cold water, the silence in the waves, each a memory etched deep in her soul.
Text.LocalizedString: In days like these, it reminds <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> of a past home, Atlantoria – the cold water, the silence in the waves, each a memory etched deep in her soul.

Text.SourceString: Today, the sea mirrors the sky, calm and serene. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> feels peace in this harmony.
Text.LocalizedString: Today, the sea mirrors the sky, calm and serene. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> feels peace in this harmony.

Text.SourceString: A swim against the current strengthens the body. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> finds joy in the water's challenge.
Text.LocalizedString: A swim against the current strengthens the body. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> finds joy in the water's challenge.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> experiments with a new kelp recipe. Though it turned out quite horrible, one must not be deterred.//<portrait=normal>The sea, after all, offers an endless array of flavors to explore.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> experiments with a new kelp recipe. Though it turned out quite horrible, one must not be deterred.//<portrait=normal>The sea, after all, offers an endless array of flavors to explore.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> foresees a visit to the market soon.//The supplies of labu and kelp in her kitchen are perilously low and in need of replenishing.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> foresees a visit to the market soon.//The supplies of labu and kelp in her kitchen are perilously low and in need of replenishing.

Text.SourceString: The gifts of the sea are not merely for taking; they are to be cherished and shared.//This is the origin of my accessories, each with its own tale of the ocean.
Text.LocalizedString: The gifts of the sea are not merely for taking; they are to be cherished and shared.//This is the origin of my accessories, each with its own tale of the ocean.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> speaks in waves, sometimes as 'I', sometimes as 'Cho Oyu'. It's a curious tide, isn't it?
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> speaks in waves, sometimes as 'I', sometimes as 'Cho Oyu'. It's a curious tide, isn't it?

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> often wonders, does she speak in third person, or is it the sea speaking through her?//<portrait=happy>Ah, such mysteries of the deep, one I cannot provide an answer to.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> often wonders, does she speak in third person, or is it the sea speaking through her?//<portrait=happy>Ah, such mysteries of the deep, one I cannot provide an answer to.

Text.SourceString: Today, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> might refer to herself as 'I', but tomorrow, who knows? The sea is full of surprises, and so am I!
Text.LocalizedString: Today, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> might refer to herself as 'I', but tomorrow, who knows? The sea is full of surprises, and so am I!

Text.SourceString: The princess, ever so sweet, carries the mischievous spark of a young dolphin. Watching over her since her little mermaid days, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> knows her playful tides well.
Text.LocalizedString: The princess, ever so sweet, carries the mischievous spark of a young dolphin. Watching over her since her little mermaid days, <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> knows her playful tides well.

Text.SourceString: Like a curious seahorse, the princess flits and floats through life.//<portrait=normal>Once, she swam up swiftly as a young merling, without her guard. The whole kingdom was in a flurry!
Text.LocalizedString: Like a curious seahorse, the princess flits and floats through life.//<portrait=normal>Once, she swam up swiftly as a young merling, without her guard. The whole kingdom was in a flurry!

Text.SourceString: Her highness, with a spirit as bubbly as sea foam, keeps <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> on her fins.
Text.LocalizedString: Her highness, with a spirit as bubbly as sea foam, keeps <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> on her fins.

Text.SourceString: The princess, a pearl nestled in the kingdom's shell. To see her mature into a sensible young mermaid is bittersweet for <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>.//In her eyes, she remains ever the little merling.
Text.LocalizedString: The princess, a pearl nestled in the kingdom's shell. To see her mature into a sensible young mermaid is bittersweet for <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>.//In her eyes, she remains ever the little merling.

Text.SourceString: Ah, Maharaja Putput, the kingdom's pufferfish, a master of mischief!//<portrait=happy>Just yesterday, he swam away with <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s favorite shell comb. Beware!
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, Maharaja Putput, the kingdom's pufferfish, a master of mischief!//<portrait=happy>Just yesterday, he swam away with <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s favorite shell comb. Beware!

Text.SourceString: Maharaja Putput, as cheeky as a sea sprite.
Text.LocalizedString: Maharaja Putput, as cheeky as a sea sprite.

Text.SourceString: Like a swift current, Maharaja Putput darts through the palace, often leaving a trail of borrowed treasures.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s seaweed scrolls were his recent prize!
Text.LocalizedString: Like a swift current, Maharaja Putput darts through the palace, often leaving a trail of borrowed treasures.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s seaweed scrolls were his recent prize!

Text.SourceString: I still haven't retrieved it until now. Gone are the seaweed scrolls.
Text.LocalizedString: I still haven't retrieved it until now. Gone are the seaweed scrolls.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s fins feel heavy right now, like they've swum through miles of deep ocean currents.//Rest calls to her like the calm after a storm.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s fins feel heavy right now, like they've swum through miles of deep ocean currents.//Rest calls to her like the calm after a storm.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> feels like a slow-moving jellyfish, more drifting than swimming. She's really looking forward to some rest.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> feels like a slow-moving jellyfish, more drifting than swimming. She's really looking forward to some rest.

Text.SourceString: On some days, everything feels quiet, even to <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>. She really needs the refreshing calm of a peaceful rest.
Text.LocalizedString: On some days, everything feels quiet, even to <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>. She really needs the refreshing calm of a peaceful rest.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> saw a seagull circling thrice earlier. She takes it as a sign – perhaps a shift in the tide is coming...or it could just be a hungry bird.//<portrait=happy>Either way, best to be prepared.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> saw a seagull circling thrice earlier. She takes it as a sign – perhaps a shift in the tide is coming...or it could just be a hungry bird.//<portrait=happy>Either way, best to be prepared.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> noticed her neighbor, the crawfish, swimming left instead of its usual right today. To her, it's surely a sign.//Perhaps it hints at unforeseen currents ahead?
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> noticed her neighbor, the crawfish, swimming left instead of its usual right today. To her, it's surely a sign.//Perhaps it hints at unforeseen currents ahead?

Text.SourceString: Last night, the stars aligned in a pattern unfamiliar to <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>. She's certain it's a sign.//<portrait=happy>Maybe it's a cosmic message, though its meaning remains a mystery.
Text.LocalizedString: Last night, the stars aligned in a pattern unfamiliar to <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>. She's certain it's a sign.//<portrait=happy>Maybe it's a cosmic message, though its meaning remains a mystery.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s soul is entwined with the Coral Tree in the kingdom. To leave it would be like a starfish severed from its arm, incomplete and yearning.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Cho Oyu</>'s soul is entwined with the Coral Tree in the kingdom. To leave it would be like a starfish severed from its arm, incomplete and yearning.

Text.SourceString: The Coral Tree is to <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> what the sun is to the day. Without it, her world would dim, like twilight falling into an endless night.
Text.LocalizedString: The Coral Tree is to <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> what the sun is to the day. Without it, her world would dim, like twilight falling into an endless night.

Text.SourceString: So, you're a dry farmer?
Text.LocalizedString: So, you're a dry farmer?

Text.SourceString: Ah, to cultivate the land, it's much like tending to a coral garden but under the sun.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> wonders, what must that feel like?
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, to cultivate the land, it's much like tending to a coral garden but under the sun.//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> wonders, what must that feel like?

Text.SourceString: Oh, you embrace the ways of the sea! <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> admires your aquatic transition. Very well done!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, you embrace the ways of the sea! <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> admires your aquatic transition. Very well done!

Special.SourceString: Not now, I'm pretty much a wet farmer now.
Special.LocalizedString: Not now, I'm pretty much a wet farmer now.

Text.SourceString: That's interesting. Cho appreciates the grower of foods, be it land or underwater.//The nurturing of life, in any form, is a noble task.
Text.LocalizedString: That's interesting. Cho appreciates the grower of foods, be it land or underwater.//The nurturing of life, in any form, is a noble task.

Text.SourceString: Do you feel the change in the water?//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> senses a storm brewing on the horizon.
Text.LocalizedString: Do you feel the change in the water?//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> senses a storm brewing on the horizon.

Text.SourceString: Ah, you are attuned to nature's whispers as well.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, you are attuned to nature's whispers as well.

Text.SourceString: What seems calm now may soon stir into a tempest. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> advises keeping a watchful eye.
Text.LocalizedString: What seems calm now may soon stir into a tempest. <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> advises keeping a watchful eye.

Special.SourceString: I don't think so, the sky is clear.
Special.LocalizedString: I don't think so, the sky is clear.

Text.SourceString: Your feelings are both here and not. Profound.
Text.LocalizedString: Your feelings are both here and not. Profound.

Text.SourceString: Has the sea ever hidden your belongings?//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> once lost her favorite shell and found it wearing a seaweed wig!
Text.LocalizedString: Has the sea ever hidden your belongings?//<NPCName>Cho Oyu</> once lost her favorite shell and found it wearing a seaweed wig!

Text.SourceString: Perhaps Maharaja Putput took them on an adventure.//<portrait=happy>Maharaja Putput has a knack for thievery as much as puffery.
Text.LocalizedString: Perhaps Maharaja Putput took them on an adventure.//<portrait=happy>Maharaja Putput has a knack for thievery as much as puffery.

Special.SourceString: I can't even find my socks!
Special.LocalizedString: I can't even find my socks!

Text.SourceString: It was quite dashing, actually. I might don it at festivals.
Text.LocalizedString: It was quite dashing, actually. I might don it at festivals.

Text.SourceString: The sea sometimes returns gifts in its own unique way.
Text.LocalizedString: The sea sometimes returns gifts in its own unique way.

Special.SourceString: I wish my lost items would come back in such a fancy way.
Special.LocalizedString: I wish my lost items would come back in such a fancy way.

Text.SourceString: Ah, silence. Well...
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, silence. Well...
